I have another one now. I'm using child tables, to build a relational setup of Companies which have many Articles (two tables).

I want to list Articles, with a bunch of filters. Some of those filters filter on Article columns, but I'm struggling to add parent row level-filters. Is it possible?

```{% set filters = "&amp;article_is_live=true&amp;parent_company_name=Apple" %}

{% for row in hubdb_table_rows(dynamic_page_hubdb_table_id, filters) %}
    ...articles belonging to apple...
{% endfor %}```
